parameters:
This is the territory of the Norde Bandits, and we won't forgive
anyone who enters without permission!

The sign is written in dirty letters... "This territory belongs to the
Norde Bandits. Anyone who enters without permission will not be
forgiven!"
Flora: "It seems there are bandits ahead..."

Liese: "Flora... If there's a man with a black eyepatch here, you
mustn't go easy on him."

Flora: "Liese-chan, did something happen...? You've been looking a bit
pale lately, I've noticed."
Liese: "I'm fine. But there's someone I absolutely cannot forgive..."
Flora: "Understood. Your enemy is my enemy as well... Let's go!"

The sign is written in crude letters... "Beyond this point lies the
territory of the Norde Bandits, and we won't forgive anyone who enters
without permission!"
Flora: "It seems there are bandits ahead..."
Flora: "We need to defeat the bandits first..."
There's nothing else to be found.
Something is lying near the stump.

Flora: "It looks like we can't dig any further... Let's come back and
try again later."
